These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, dubstep, gospel, classical
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | dubstep | indie | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, fish, chinchilla, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | snake | chinchilla | fish | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, magic-tricks, fishing, writing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | fishing | video-games | magic-tricks | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, boat, train
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | boat | snowmobile | subway | train |

 #################################

 
