1. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3       |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama | zombie | crime |

